# Keep the image build context tiny: the Dockerfiles COPY pre-built release
# binaries (the eBPF object is already embedded), so send only those — not the
# multi-GB target/ tree or the source.
*
!target
target/*
!target/release
target/release/*
!target/release/velstra
!target/release/velstra-cni
!target/release/velstra-controller
